I. Number series
THE SUM OF SERIES 1/2!+2/3!+3/4!+4/5!+.....N/(N+1)!
INPUT
n=int(input("enter number of terms"))
f=1
s=0
for i in range (1,n+1):
    f=f*(i+1)
    s=s*(i/f)
print("sum:",s)

OUTPUT
